phrases: Are you human or a Corpse?!
I did not turn into a Corpse!
The piercing gun was a success!
When I increased the explosives, the metal steam became pointed like a needle!
I stopped the virus right at the neck.
It is exactly what we studied.
We might be able to save people who have been bitten now.
I calculate about 8.7 kilometers to Iron Fortress.
How long are we going to wait here?!
We have to head for the Iron Fortress soon, or we will not make it!
But my father said to wait for his signal.
There will not be a signal!
As long as the lord is absent, we must obey Ayame-sama in his stead.
Why am I wasting my time with you children?
I will not wait any longer.
We are going off on our own.
You are still arguing about this?
We would be waiting here till dawn.
I would appreciate it if you kept your hands to yourself.
Is there anyone here who can run a Railfort?
I am just a trainee though.
What is so hard about moving something along a rail?
I will make a path, so just follow me.
Oh, well, as long as I keep it close range.
Let us try for 100 seconds, then.
We have to escape while we can!
And you are the last one!
If we can mass-produce these guns, we will be able to fight the Corpses!
First, we need to meet up with everyone else.
Do not push, I was here first!
Let passengers on before the cargo!
Shut up and let me on!
It is okay, we are humans!
Then show us that you do not have any bite marks.
I will explain it to them.
If they see me take out the Corpses, they will have to accept me!
I mean... you are really strong.
You are not normal, are you?
The passenger car is in the depot!
It will not leave until you are all on board!
They just followed me on their own.
You are getting on too, are not you?
You are supposed to be in jail.
Yeah, you almost got me killed.
That is why you were able to get out of your cell.
I have been saying it this whole time.
Why are we getting on at the very back?
I want to be near the boiler.
Once it is ready, the next step is ignition.
Seems like you got it to go.
Nameless -san... thank you for your help earlier.
Ayame-san, you are not much for war, are you?
That is why so many people die.
We will have you guard the rear cars.
That is not what I was planning.
You are going to have to handle things on your own for now.
Considering all of that fighting she had to do...
Do you see my father anywhere?
We did not follow the proper departure procedure.
If we rush it, the furnace could break.
Are we going to be okay?
I am just filling in too!
With this piercing gun, we can...
I knew I should have killed you earlier.
Stop talking like you are human, Corpse!
Kurusu-sama, incoming Corpses at the front!
Kurusu, are there many of them?
Run over any Corpse in the way!
The drawbridge will not lower at this rate!
The Iron Fortress will not be able to move if we run out of water.
What are you going to do, Kurusu?
There is a manual lever in front of the bridge.
I will use it to drop the bridge.
You are going to go outside?!
If we do not put our lives on the line now, then when are we supposed to?
There is someone with the Corpses!
Then why is he fighting the Corpses?
Watch as the man you cast out spills his blood and dies.
Let us give him a hand.
We cannot sit here and do nothing.
If we open the door, the Corpses could...
They are just killing each other.
I want you to live the rest of your lives knowing the man you abandoned saved you.
And I will laugh at you from the afterlife.
And tell you that it serves you right!
What the hell are you thinking?!
Why would you save a Corpse?!
We already brought you on board.
I feel no shame being saved by you.
If you still have any humanity left, you will kill yourself for everyone is sake!
Although, he is not human either.
When I cannot see anything ahead
And slam everything onto the ground
My soul is devoted to my friend
That connect you make a sound
There are just dreams in the same rain
I am tired of getting answers
The ideal only has its doors
City is uplifted and drown in noise
I will still sing and stop turning the rudder
